n sintáctica: reformulación, reinterpretación, reserva y otras relaciones argumentativas. Por último, se adentra en la aplicación del modelo a clases de palabras, funciones y oraciones, ofreciendo, así, una descripción detenida que permite ser extendida a otros campos.  aThis work offers a substantial advance in the study of the macrosyntax of Spanish. Situated in the field of discourse realization, it provides theoretical foundations and a precise methodology. It describes the units of discourse, the new categories that must be taken into account to describe speech (operators, connectors and constructions), and integrates the diachronic aspect, in a dynamic vision of the language.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 4aDiskurs. 4aKommunikation / Sprache. 4aSpanisch. 4aSyntax. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / Syntax.2bisacsh  aSpanish.  acommunication.  adiscourse.  asyntax.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2024 Part 1z97831113321920 cEPUBz97831113157990 cprintz978311131485340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311131545440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783111315454423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783111315454/original  a978-3-11-133219-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2024 Part 1b2024  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles